(24, 1, '2019-02-02 15:11:19', '2019-02-02 15:11:19', '<h4>Hello Viewers</h4>		\n			<h2>I am Sudipta Das. Find Me deeper in here.</h2>		\n			<a href=\"https://sudiptaprof.com/about/\" target=\"_blank\" role=\"button\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n						About Me\n					</a>\n			<a href=\"https://sudiptaprof.com/projects/\" target=\"_blank\" role=\"button\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n						My Projects\n					</a>\n			<h4>Why Choose Me</h4>		\n			<h2>Find Me interesting</h2>		\n				<h3>\n					Vision\n				</h3>\n				<p>What is the use in developing code, when it won’t be applicable a year or two down the road? I want to create code and libraries that are open to refactoring, and easy to use in all code languages.</p>\n				<h3>\n					Teamwork\n				</h3>\n				<p>Learning how to work as a team in college is one way to get over that “hermit” image…and working as a team online or in the office can only produce stellar projects and I am a very good tea player.</p>\n				<h3>\n					Experience\n				</h3>\n				<p>Beyond hands-on experience, you might also be addicted to math and science, and the ability to stay organized. In my career I experienced how to become professional.</p>\n				<h3>\n					Learning\n				</h3>\n				<p>I am still learning. i am always interested learning new things and i am passionate about it. I may fail but I do not leave it. I love to take challenges.</p>\n			<h4>Important Pages</h4>		\n			<h2>Pages to get you started Right Away</h2>		\n										<img width=\"945\" height=\"536\" src=\"https://sudiptaprof.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/elementor-compatible.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://sudiptaprof.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/elementor-compatible.png 945w, https://sudiptaprof.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/elementor-compatible-300x170.png 300w, https://sudiptaprof.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/elementor-compatible-768x436.png 768w, https://sudiptaprof.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/elementor-compatible-600x340.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 945px) 1